Dewboy, Cybertron was not organic! Ever! The Quintessons built the planet, 
there is nothing or very little organic. In G1 in Rebirth, in the core was 
some thing that scoruge activated to deactivate every transformer. Want to 
know whats odd? The core was all metallic. It was a big factorish type thing. 
There is no orghanic core on cybertron. End of story.
